quran[269]{c,v,t}:
  18,75,"Inna: \"day ur ak nni$ ara, keçç, s tidep, ur tezmiôev, yidi, a pûebôev, d awez$i"
  18,76,"Inna: \"ma steqsa$ k $ef t$awsa, deffir ta, ur teddu yidi. Ni$ ssutre$ ak d ssmaê"
  18,77,"Lêan, armi bbwven ar imezda$ n yiwet n temdint, ssutren asen lqut. Ugin a ten snubgten. Ufan en lêiv, qôib ad i$li. Iûeggem it. Inna: \"ma teb$iv, tzemrev a ppepwaxellûev $ef waya"
  18,78,"Inna: \"Tura a nemfaôaq. Ad ak d fke$ lmaâna n wayen i$ef ur tezmirev a pûebôev, d awez$i"
  18,79,"Lbabuô nni, n igellilen i ixedmen di yill. B$i$ a t ôée$, acku yiwen ugellid, deffir sen, itekkes yal lbabuô, s yi$il"
  18,80,"Wanag ileméi nni, llan imawlan is d lmumnin. Nugad ad iêeppem fellasen tinufqa, tijehli"
  18,81,"Neb$a ad asen d Irr, Mass nnsen, it yifen: win iûfan, iqeôben nezzeh aêunu"
  18,82,"Wanag lêiv, n sin warrac igujilen n temdint. Illa ugerruj seddaw as, i nitni. Babat sen d argaz ilhan. Mass ik Ib$a, ard im$uôen, ara d ssuff$en agerruj nnsen. D aêunu s$uô Mass ik. Ur t xdime$ s lameô iw. D tagi ay d lmaâna n wayen i$ef ur tezmiôev a pûebôev"
  18,83,"Steqsan k $ef Bu sin wacciwen. Ini: \"ad awen d awi$, fellas, asmekti"
  18,84,"S tidep, Nefka yas di tmurt, u Nsehhel as iberdan di yal cci"
  18,85,Iîîef yiwen n ubrid
  18,86,"armi sanda i$elli yiîij. Iufa i$elli $ef tala ilu$en. Iufa n $uôes agdud. Nenna: \"a Bu sin wacciwen, âaqeb iten, ne$ lhu $uôsen"
  18,87,"Inna: \"win idensen a t nâaqeb, sinna, ad iu$al ar Mass is at Iâaqeb aâaqeb unekkaô"
  18,88,"Wanag i win iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, akafi igerzen. Ad as Nini i isehlen si lameô nne£"
  18,89,"Sinna, ilêa d yiwen n ubrid"
  18,90,"armi sanda d ineqqeô yiîij. Iufa n ineqqeô ed $ef ugdud, iwumi ur Nefki ar at isdarin segs"
  18,91,Am akka. Ni$ ibbwev a£ d akw usali s
  18,92,"Sinna, idda d yiwen n ubrid"
  18,93,"armi ibbwev ger sin iêdiden. Iufa, deffir sen, agdud qôib ur fehhmen awal"
  18,94,"Nnan: \"a Bu sin wacciwen, s tidep, Iaouo akked Maouo la ssefsaden di tmurt. A k nxelleû ma terriv ûûuô garane$ yidsen"
  18,95,"Inna: \"yif it iyi Ifka Mass iw. Efket iyi afus, ad rre$ ûûuô garawen yidsen"
  18,96,"Awit iyi d tiqaùmtin n wuzzal alamma irgel wayen illan ger idurar\". Inna: \"ûuvet alamma tekker degs tmes. Awit iyi d ad smire$ fellas nnêas ifsin"
  18,97,"D$a ur zmiren a t id zegren, ur zmiren a t id flun"
  18,98,"Inna: \"ayagi d aêunu s$uô Mass iw. Mi d tusa lemâahda n Mass iw, a t Isawi. Lemâahda n Mass iw d tidep"
  18,99,"Assen, a ten Neoo ad ddehmen wa $ef wa. Aûuvu di lbuq, d$a a ten Nessemlil akw"
  18,100,"A d Nessken nezzeh Loahennama, assen, i ijehliyen"
  18,101,"wid iwumi sêurrment wallen nnsen, mgal asmekti W. Llan ur zmiren i usemêes"
  18,102,"Day $ilen, wid ijehlen, ad rren imdanen iW, d imawlan war Nek? Ih, Nhegga Loahennama, d axxam i ijehliyen"
  18,103,"Ini: \"ad awen mle$ at igiten imexsuôen sennig wiyav"
  18,104,"Wid iwumi iweddeô laâtab nnsen di tmeddurt n ddunit, wanag nitni nwan gerzen igi"
  18,105,"Widak d wid i inekôen issekniyen n Mass nnsen, akked temlilit yideS. Mêan igiten nnsen. Ur ten Nwezzen, ass n tnekra"
  18,106,"Atan uqeîîi nnsen: Loahennama, imi jehlen, u mmaâlken deg issekniyen iW, akked imazanen iW"
  18,107,"Ma d wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, axxam nnsen d leonanat n Loennet"
  18,108,"Degs ad wekkôen, ur ssuturen ayen nniven"
  18,109,"Ini: \"lemmer ill d lmidad, i wawalen n Mass iw, ad iqqaô yill, uqbel ad fukken wawalen n Mass iw, xas a d nawi i t icban n lmidad"
  18,110,"Ini: \"nek d amdan kan, am kunwi. Weêêan iyi d ar Öebbi nnwen, d Öebbi Yiwen. Win issaramen timlilit n Mass is, ad ixdem ayen ilhan, ur ipcarak yiwen deg waâbad n Mass is"
  19,1,Khiâû
  19,2,"Asmekti uêunu n Mass ik, i umdan iS Zakarya"
  19,3,"mi iger, i Mass is, ti$ôi tabavnit"
  19,4,"Inna: \"a Mass iw! S tidep, ôéent laâvam iw, aqeôôu iôeq si ccib. A Mass iw! Anuju $uôeK uroin iyi isnu$ben"
  19,5,"Nek ugade$ llzem iw, deffir i. Tameîîut iw d tiâiqeôt. Efk iyi d lfeôx s$uôeK"
  19,6,"ad iyi iwôet, ad iwôet si twacult n Yaâqub. Err it, a Mass iw, d win iôuvan"
  19,7,"A Zakarya, s tidep, Nbecceô ik s uqcic, ism is Yeêya. Ur Nefki, i yiwen, ism agi, uqbel is"
  19,8,"Inna: \"a Mass iw! Amek ara sâu$ aqcic, tameîîut iw d tiâiqeôt, u nek $emqe$ di tewser"
  19,9,"Inna: \"Akka. Inna d Mass ik: ayagi ishel fellI. Ni$ Xelqe$ k, zik, ur telliv d acemma"
  19,10,"Inna: \"a Mass iw! Efk iyi d assekni\". Inna: \"assekni ik, ur tepmeslayev i medden, krav wavan, ur tuvnev"
  19,11,"Iffe$ ed ar ugdud is, si lemqam. Iweêêa yasen ad anzen ûûbeê, tameddit"
  19,12,"A Yeêya, eîîef Tazmamt, s loehd\". D ûûebyan, Nefka yas ûûwab"
  19,13,"lmaênana akked ûûfawa, s$uône£. Ipêezzib"
  19,14,ibedd i imawlan is; ur illi d aqehhaô ne$ d amâaûi
  19,15,"Tifrat fellas asmi d ilul, asmi ara immet, asmi ara d iu$al d amuddir"
  19,16,"Smekti d, di Tezmamt, Meryem, asmi taâzel iman is, si twacult is, di tama ugmuv"
  19,17,"Terra ssteô garas yidsen. Nuzen as d ôôuê nne£. £uôes, amzun d amdan ifuqen"
  19,18,"Tenna: \"ad iyi Ëerz Uênin, segk, ma tepêezzibev"
  19,19,"Inna: \"nek, d amersul kan n Mass im, ad am fke$ aqcic iûfan"
  19,20,"Tenna: \"amek ara sâu$ aqcic, ur iyi innul umdan, ur lli$ d tazennant"
  19,21,"Inna: \"Akka. Inna d Mass im: ayagi, ishel fellI. A t Nerr d assekni i medden, d aêunu s$uône£. D lameô ippuêeppmen"
  19,22,"Tebbwi tadist; syis taâzel iman is, di tama ibaâden"
  19,23,"Bdan p id inzikmiren ar loedra n tezdayt. Tenna: \"anna$ lemmer mmute$, uqbel ayagi, ad pwappu$ akw"
  19,24,"Issawel as d, seddaw as: \"kkes a$wbel, ih, Mass im Irra i$éeô, seddaw am"
  19,25,"Hucc, ar $uôem, loedra n tezdayt, ad am d i$li ppmeô amaynut ibwan"
  19,26,"Eçç, ssew, ssefôeê iéôi m. Ma twalav yiwen n umdan, ini as: nek, s tidep, uéame$ i Uênin, ur pmeslaye$, assa, i umdan"
  19,27,"Tôuê yis ar ugdud is, tebbwi t. Nnan: \"a Meryem! Ni$ tusiv d, s temsalt ihejjnen"
  19,28,"A ultmas n Haôun, ur illi baba m d argaz ucmit, ur telli imma m d tazennant"
  19,29,"Teswâad $uôes. Nnan: \"amek ara nemmeslay i ûûebyan di dduê"
  19,30,"Inna: \"nek d amdan n Öebbi. Ifka yi d Tazmamt. Irra yi d nnbi"
  19,31,"Iôqa yi anda lli$. Iweûûa yi taéallit, u zzakat, skud mazal iyi d amuddir"
  19,32,"Ad bedde$ i yimma. Ur iyi Irri d aqehhaô, ne$ d ccaqi"
  19,33,"Tifrat felli asmi d lule$, asmi ara mmte$, asmi ara d u$ale$ d amuddir"
  19,34,"D wagi ay d Âisa, mmi s n Meryem. D awal n tidep, i$ef cukken"
  19,35,"Ur iûwib ara, i Öebbi, ad Isâu kra n mmi S. Gedha syiS! Ma Iseyya lameô, ad as Yini kan: \"ili\"! Ad yili"
  19,36,"Öebbi, s tidep, d Mass iw, d Mass nnwen. Ihi, âabdet eP. D wagi ay d abrid uwqim"
  19,37,"Mgarraden ikabaren garasen. A tawa$it n wid ijehlen, mara walin ass abarar"
  19,38,"Ara slen, ara walin, ass ideg ara d asen $uône£! Maca, imednas, assa, di ttelfan s ûûeê"
  19,39,"Nabi ten, $ef ass n ssixîa, mara iûaô lameô. Nitni, di l$eflan, nitni ur uminen"
  19,40,"Ih, d Nekwni, ara Iweôten tamurt akked wayen illan fellas. £uône£ tu$alin nnsen"
  19,41,"Smekti d, di Tezmamt, Ibôahim. Ih, Neppa, illa d bab n tidep, d nnbi"
  19,42,"Mi inna i baba s: \"a baba! Acimi tâabdev win ur nsell, ur nepwali, ur k ip$itin s wacemma"
  19,43,"Ih, a baba, Nek ippunefk iyi d, si tmusni, ayen ur ak neppunefk. Ihi ddu yidi, a k nhu$ ar ubrid ilhan"
  19,44,A baba! Ur âabbed Cciîan. Ni$ Cciîan illa d amâaûu i Uênin
  19,45,"A baba! Nek, ugade$ a k iwwet uâaqeb n Uênin, a ppiliv d ameddakwel n Cciîan"
  19,46,"Inna d: \"day tugiv keçç, a Ibôahim, iôebbiten iw? Ma ur tfukkev ara, war ccekk, a k ôeome$! Ïixxeô iyi tallit $wezzifen"
  19,47,"Inna: \"ili di tifrat. Ad ssutre$ i Mass iw, ad ak Isemmeê. Neppa, s tidep, Iâuzz iyi"
  19,48,"Ad âazle$ iman iw segwen, akked wayen tepnujum, war Öebbi. Ad naâôe$ Mass iw, ahat, s unuju w, ar Mass iw, ur $webne$ ara"
  19,49,"Mi iaâzel iman is segsen akked wayen âabden, war Öebbi, Nefka yas Isêaq akked Yaâqub. Yal yiwen, Nerra t d nnbi"
  19,50,"Nefka yasen seg uêunu nne£. Nerna yasen ccekôan umâin, lfayeq"
  19,51,"Smekti d, di Tezmamt, Musa. Ih, neppa, illa d aâeôvi, d amazan, d nnbi"
  19,52,"Nessawel as d, si îîeôf ayeffus n udrar. Nessqeôb it id, ad as Nmel"
  19,53,"Nefka yas, seg uêunu nne£, gma s, Haôun, d nnbi"
  19,54,"Smekti d, di Tezmamt, Ismaâil. Ih, neppa, illa d win ippaîafen di lemâahda s, d amazan, d nnbi"
  19,55,"Iumeô i twacult is, taéallit, zzakat. Iôuva t Mass is"
  19,56,"Smekti d, di Tezmamt, Idris. Ih, neppa, illa d bab n tidep, d nnbi"
  19,57,Nessuli t s amkan aâlayen
  19,58,"D wigi i I$at Öebbi, ger lambiyya, ger tarwa n Adem, ger wid i Nebbwi akked Nuê, ger tarwa n Ibôahim, akked Isôail, ger wid Nenha u Nefren. Ma $ôan asen issekniyen n Uênin, ad $lin knan, s imeîîawen"
  19,59,"Lxwelf nnsen d asatu i iooan taéallit, ddan d ccehwiyyat. Ad magren ttelfan"
  19,60,"Kkes ed wid isteôoâen, iumnen, xeddmen ayen ilhan. Wigi, ad kecmen Loennet, ur pwadensen s wacemma"
  19,61,"Leonanat n Âaden i Iwaââed Uênin, i imdanen iS, di tbavnit. Lemâahda S, s tidep, a ppevôu"
  19,62,"Ur sellen, degs, i yir awal, siwa: \"tifrat\"! Dinna, lqut nnsen, ûûbeê, tameddit"
  19,63,"D tagi ay d Loennet, ara Nerr d lweôt, i wid ipêezziben, seg imdanen nne£"
  19,64,"Ur d nepûubbu, siwa ma s lameô n Mass ik. IneS i illan zdat nne$, i illan deffir nne$, akked wayen illan garasen. Mass ik ur Iteppu"
  19,65,"Mass n tmurt, igenwan, akked wayen illan garasen. Ihi, âabed iT, ili d imezgi deg uâbad iS. Day tesnev win isâan ism iS"
  19,66,"La iqqaô umdan: \"ma mmute$, day a yi d ssuff$en d amuddir"
  19,67,"Day ur icfa ara umdan, ar t id Nxelq, zik, ur illi d acemma"
  19,68,"S Mass ik, ara ten Nefser, nitni akked cwaîen. Sinna, a ten Nerr ad zzin i Loahennama, $ef tgwecrar"
  19,69,"Sinna, a d Nekkes, si yal arbaâ, wid ibe$wven nezzeh, ar Uênin"
  19,70,"Sinna, d Nekwni, war ccekk, i Isnen sennig akw, imenza ar tmeô$iwt"
  19,71,"Akken tellam, a pqeôbem $uôes. Akka, ar Mass ik, d aseyyi imuêeppmen"
  19,72,"Sinna, a Nsellek wid ipêezziben. A Neoo degs, imednas, $ef tgwecrar"
  19,73,"Mara asen $ôen issekniyen iberrzen nne£, qqaôen wid ijehlen i wid iumnen: \"menyif sin irebbuyaâ di temâict akw i lemwansa"
  19,74,"Acêal isuta i Nesqucc, uqbel nnsen, ifen ten tarkunt, ûûifa"
  19,75,"Ini: \"ad Irnu Uênin di laâmeô, i im$eôôqen, alamma walan acu i sen ippuwaââden: d aâaqeb ne$ d imir. Ad éôen anwa illan deg umkan adiran mavi, ay d bu lâaskeô uôhifen mavi"
  19,76,"Ad Irnu Öebbi nnhaya i wid ipwanhan. Ar Mass ik, leûlaê idumen ifen akafi, asisi"
  19,77,"Ma twalav win iugin issekniyen nne£, u inna: \"tarkunt, tarwa ad iyi ppunefkent, war ccekk"
  19,78,"Aâni issen tabavnit, ne$ iu$ lemâahda s$uô Uênin"
  19,79,"Xaîi, a Naru ayen inna. Ad as Nessi$wzef nezzeh aâaqeb"
  19,80,"A Newôet ay d inna, a d ias $uône£, d awêid"
  19,81,"Xtaôen, war Öebbi, iôebbiten ar asen d iawin tazmert"
  19,82,"Xaîi! Ad nekôen aâbad nnsen, ad asen u$alen d ixûimen"
  19,83,"Ur twalav ara, Nuzen ed ccwaîen i ijehliyen, la ten laâjen s ljuô"
  19,84,"Ur pêiri fellasen, la Nessalay kan leêsab nnsen"
  19,85,"Ass ideg ara Nefser wid ipêezziben ar Uênin, d imaâôaven"
  19,86,"a Nenheô ijehliyen, d aqwvaô, ar Loahennama"
  19,87,"Ur sâin ccafuâa, siwa win iu$en lemâahda ar Uênin"
  19,88,"Nnan: \"Isâa Uênin, aqcic"
  19,89,Ni$ tebbwim d abeââuq
  19,90,"Segs, qôib flan igenwan, tcerreg tmurt, grurjen idurar s édiê"
  19,91,"Gren aS mmi S, i Uênin"
  19,92,"Ur iwjib ara, i Uênin, ad Isâu mmi S"
  19,93,"Akken llan di tmurt akked igenwan, siwa ay d iteddun, ar Uênin, s waâbad"
  19,94,"Ih, Iêseb iten, Issen nezzeh amvan nnsen"
  19,95,"Akw a d asen $uôeS, ass n tnekra, yiwen yiwen"
  19,96,"War ccekk, wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, a ten Iâuzz Uênin"
  19,97,"Nerra t kan d ushil, s tmeslayt ik, iwakken a pbeccôev, syis, wid iêezzben, u a pnedôev agdud iggernenn"
  19,98,"Acêal isuta ay Nesqucc uqbel nnsen! Day a pmagrev yiwen degsen, ne$ a ppeslev i uswecwec nnsen"
  20,1,Ïh
  20,2,Ur ak d Nessader ara Leqwôan iwakken a p$weblev
  20,3,D asmekti kan i win ippagwaden
  20,4,D tarusi s$uô Win Ixelqen tamurt akked igenwan aâlayen
  20,5,Aênin i Iâanncen $ef usgeld
  20,6,"IneS i illan deg igenwan, i illan di tmurt, i illan garasen, i illan seddaw tmurt"
  20,7,"Ma téaâvev, ihi, Neppa Iéôa sser, akked wayen iffren sennig es"
  20,8,"Öebbi, ur illi ôebbi siwa Neppa. IneS ismawen imxulaf"
  20,9,Ma tusa k id teqûiî n Musa
  20,10,"Mi iwala times, inna i twacult is: \"qqimet dagi, nek wala$ times. Amar awen d awi$, segs, asafu, ne$ ad afe$, di tmes, nnhaya"
  20,11,"Mi ibbwev $uôes, Ssawlen as d: \"a Musa"
  20,12,"Nek, s tidep, d Mass ik. Ekkes arkasen ik, ih, aql ak di Ïuwa, ta$zut iôqan"
  20,13,"Nek Smenyafe$ k, sell ed i uweêêi"
  20,14,"Nek, s tidep, d Öebbi, ur illi ôebbi siwa Nek. Ihi, âabed iyI, ééal ilmend usmekti W"
  20,15,"Imir, s tidep, a d ias. B$i$ a t Ffre$, iwakken yal yiwen a t Nkafi $ef wayen ixdem"
  20,16,"£uôek a k issefôe$ fellas, win ur numin ara yis, i iddan d lhawiyya s! Mulac a pnegrev"
  20,17,"D acu p tinna deg ufus ayeffus ik, a Musa"
  20,18,"Inna: \"d taâkwazt iw, fellas tekkaye$, syis sse$laye$ d iferrawen i lmal iw. Sseqdace$ p i wayen nniven"
  20,19,"Inna: \"veggeô ip, a Musa"
  20,20,"Iveggeô ip, tu$al d azrem, ippeênunuf"
  20,21,"Inna: \"ddem ip, ur ppagwad, ad as Nerr udem is amenzu"
  20,22,"Eémev afus ik, s idis ik. A d iffe$ d amellal, ur ihlik. D assekni nniven"
  20,23,"iwakken ad ak Nessken, seg issekniyen nne£ imeqwôaêanen"
  20,24,"Öuê ar Ferâun. Neppa, s tidep, d aqehhaô"
  20,25,"Inna: \"a Mass iw! Lli idmaren iw"
  20,26,Sehhel iyi lameô iw
  20,27,Efsi tiyersi seg iles iw
  20,28,ad fehmen awal iw
  20,29,Efk iyi amâiwen di twacult iw
  20,30,gma Haôun
  20,31,"Ssem$weô, syis, tazmert iw"
  20,32,Zdukkel it ar lameô iw
  20,33,iwakken a K nesbuccaâ aîas
  20,34,a K id nesmekti aîas
  20,35,"Keçç, s tidep, la $ d Tepwaliv"
  20,36,"Inna: \"tepwaqbel tuppra k, a Musa"
  20,37,"Ni$ Nâateq ik, tikelt nniven"
  20,38,"mi Nweêêa, i yimma k, ayen i Nweêêa"
  20,39,"err it deg usenduq, veggeô it s asif. A t issers wasif deg uqeôqaô, a t iddem ucengu W, u d acengu is. Fki$ ak si lmaênana W, a ppeppuôebbiv zdat wallen iW"
  20,40,"Mi telêa ultma k, tenna: \"ma ad awen mle$ w ara itkelfen fellas\"? Nerra k id i yimma k, ad fukken imeîîawen is, ur têezzen ara. Ten$iv amdan, Nsellek ik si le$wben. Njeôôeb ik s lfetnat. Tzed$ev kra iseggwasen ar at Madian. Sinna, tusiv d s lqwedôa, a Musa"
  20,41,Smenyafe$ k i iman iW
  20,42,"Öuêet, keçç akked gma k, s issekniyen iW, ur stehzayet $ef usmekti W"
  20,43,"Öuêet ar Ferâun. Neppa, s tidep, d aqehhaô"
  20,44,"Mmeslayet as s wawal amelêan, amar a d immekti, ne$ ad iagwad"
  20,45,"Nnan: \"a Mass nne$! Nugad ad a$ iglez, ne$ ad ijuô"
  20,46,"Inna: \"ur ppagwadet, Nek, war ccekk, yidwen, Selle$, Pwali"
  20,47,"Öuêet $uôes, tinem as: \"nekwni d imazanen n Mass ik, seddu yidne$ At Isôail, ur ten ppâaqab ara. Aql a$ nusa k id s issekniyen n Mass ik. Tifrat i wi iddan d nnhaya"
  20,48,"S tidep, neppuweêêa d, ar ad ippuâaqeb win inekôen, iwexxôen"
  20,49,"Inna: \"anwa T Mass nnwen, a Musa"
  20,50,"Inna: \"Mass nne$ d Win Ifkan lxelq is i yal cci, sinna, Inha"
  20,51,"Inna: \"amek tevôa d isuta timezwura"
  20,52,"Inna: \"i ten Iéôan, d Mass iw, di Tezmamt. Mass iw ur I$ellev, ur Iteppu"
  20,53,Win i wen irran tamurt d dduê. Iga yawen degs iberdan. Issers ed aman seg igenni. Nessuffu$ ed yissen tiyugiwin n yal ûûenf n le$ôus
  20,54,"Eççet, ekset lmal nnwen. Deg waya, s tidep, d issekniyen i imawlan n ddehn"
  20,55,"Segs, Nxelq ikwen; degs, a kwen Nerr; segs, a kwen id Nessuffe$, tikelt nniven"
  20,56,"Ni$ Nessken as akw issekniyen nne£ inkeô, iugi"
  20,57,"Inna: \"day a$ d tusiv, s ssêur ik, a Musa, ad a$ tessuff$ev seg wakal nne"
  20,58,"War ccekk, ad ak d nawi ssêur i t icban. Err garane$ yidek ppaâud, deg umekkan iwulmen, ur t nezgal, ur t tezgalev"
  20,59,"Inna: \"ppaâud nnwen ass n tme$ôa, a d mlilen medden, di tûebêit"
  20,60,"Izzi Ferâun, ijmaâ ed ccbukat is, d$a iusa d"
  20,61,"Inna yasen Musa:\"a tawa$it nnwen! Ur d garet tikerkas $ef Öebbi, a kwen Isxev s uâaqeb. Ni$ ad ixseô win d igren"
  20,62,"Mcawaôen f lameô nnsen, ffren ayen mmeslayen"
  20,63,"Nnan: \"ihi, sin agi d iseêêaren, b$an a kwen ssuff$en seg wakal nnwen, s ssêur nnsen. Ad kksen abrid nnwen amxallef"
  20,64,"Jemâat ed ccbukat nnwen, sinna aset ed d leûfuf. Ni$ ad irbeê, assa, win iufraren"
  20,65,"Nnan: \"a Musa! A pveggôev keçç, ne$ d nekwni ara iveggôen d imezwura"
  20,66,"Inna: \"xaîi, veggôet\"! Si ssêur nnsen, iwala amzun leêêun imraren akked tâakwzin nnsen"
  20,67,"Musa, deg iman is, iêus i lxuf"
  20,68,"Nenna: \"ur ppagwad! Keçç, s tidep, sennig sen"
  20,69,"Veggeô i illan deg ufus ik ayeffus! Ad isseblaâ ay d snulfan\". Ay d snulfan, siwa ccbukat iseêêaren. Anda idda useêêar, ur irebbeê ara"
  20,70,"£¨lin iseêêaren, knan, nnan: \"numen s Mass n Haôun akked Musa"
  20,71,"Inna: \"day tumnem yiS, uqbel i wen serrêe$? Neppa, zi$, d ameqwôan nnwen. Isêefv awen ssêur. War ccekk, ad awen gezme$, avaô sya, afus sya, u a kwen ûemmôe$ af umidag n leodar n tezdayin. A ppeéôem, s tidep, anwa ay d bab uâaqeb meqqwôen, u ara idumen sennig wiyav"
  20,72,"Nnan: \"ur k nesmenyaf, d awez$i, i wayen i $ d iusan ubeggen, akw i Win i $ Ixelqen. Seyyi i k ihwan a pseyyiv. Aseyyi k, d aseyyi $ef tmeddurt n ddunit agi kan"
  20,73,"Ih, numen s Mass nne$, iwakken ad a$ Isemmeê tuccva nne$, akked wayen n ssêur i têeppmev fellane$. Pifxiô Öebbi d Imezgi"
  20,74,"Ih, Loahennama i win iusan ar Mass is, d abe$wvi. Ur ipmeppat degs, ur d ippidir"
  20,75,"Win i iusan $uôeS d lmumen u ixdem ayen ilhan, widak ad ilin deg imukan aâlayen mavi"
  20,76,"leonanat n Âaden, ddawat sen isaffen ppazzalen, ad wekkôen din. Ayagi, d akafi i win zeddigen"
  20,77,"Ni$ Nweêêa i Musa: \"ôuê, deg iv, akked imdanen iW. Egg asen abrid akiwan, di yill. Ur ppagwad a kwen in vefôen, ur ppiwêic"
  20,78,"Ferâun, s iâsekôiwen is, vefôen ten. Isseblaâ ten yill, içça ten"
  20,79,"Itlef Ferâun agdud is, ur inhi"
  20,80,"A yAt Isôail! Ni$ Nsellek ikwen seg ucangu nnwen. Nefka yawen ppaâud, ar loiha tayeffus n udrar. Nessers awen d lmenna, ifeôôuoen"
  20,81,"Eççet si lmakla ilhan, i s ikwen N$at. Ur zegret tilas fellas, mulac a kwen immager urrif iW. Win immuger urrif iW, ni$ igrareb"
  20,82,"U Nek, s tidep, Psemmiêe$ i win isteôoâen, iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, d$a ipwanha"
  20,83,"Acu i k i$eûben seg ugdud ik, a Musa"
  20,84,"Inna: \"zgan deffir i. £awle$ d $ureK, a Mass iw, iwakken a Pôaviv"
  20,85,"Inna: \"ih, ni$ Njeôôeb agdud ik, deffir ek. Itelf iten Usamiri"
  20,86,"Iu$al ed Musa s agdud is, s zzâaf d wumri. Inna: \"a yagdud iw! Day ur awen Ifka ara, Mass nnwen, lemâahda lâali? Day tâaîîel fellawen lemâahda? Ne$ day teb$am a kwen immager urrif n Mass nnwen? Tzeglem ppaâud iw"
  20,87,"Nnan: \"ur nezgil ppaâud ik, s leb$i nne$. Maca, nbubb tiâakkwmin n ôôêuê n ugdud, d$a nveggeô iten. Akken i iveggeô Usamiri"
  20,88,"Issuffe$ asen d aâejmi, d ameslux isrugmuten. Nnan: \"wagi d ôebbi nnwen u d ôebbi n Musa. Ippu"
  20,89,"Day ur walan ara, ur asen d ippara awal, ur izmir a ten ivuôô, ne$ a ten infaâ"
  20,90,"Ni$ Haôun inna yasen, uqbel: \"a yagdud iw! Teppuhewwlem kan, yis. Mass nnwen, s tidep, d Aênin. Ddut yidi, vefôet lameô iw"
  20,91,"Nnan: \"ur tnepfukku akaber is, d awez$i, alamma iu$al ed Musa $uône"
  20,92,"Inna: \"a Haôun! D acu i k iîîfen, mi ten twalav nnetlafen"
  20,93,Day ur teddiv ara yidi? Day tugiv lameô iw
  20,94,"Inna: \"a mmi s n yimma! Ur iyi ppaîîaf si tamart iw, ne$ seg uqeôôu w. Nek, s tideps, ugade$ ad iyi d tiniv: tessemfaôaqev At Isôail, ur tu$ev awal iw"
  20,95,"Inna: \"d acu t leqsed ik a Usamiri"
  20,96,"Inna: \"wala$ ayen ur walan. Ddme$ d tummeét n lateô umazan, veggôe$ p. Akka ay êusse$ deg iman iw"
  20,97,"Inna: \"ôuê ihi, a ppevôu yidek di tmeddurt a ppeqqaôev: ur iyi pnalet! U, s tidep, $uôek ppaâud ik ur tezmirev a t tzeglev. Muqel ôebbi ik, u$uô mazal teqqimev, ard a t nesseô$, a t ssebruzzaâ ar yill, wakali"
  20,98,"Mass nnwen, siwa Öebbi. Ur illi ôebbi siwa Neppa. Tamusni S tjemmel yal cci"
  20,99,"Akka i k Nêekku, seg isallen n zik. Ni$ Nefka yak d, s$uône£, asmekti"
  20,100,"Win i s iwexxôen, ad iâabbi taâkkwemt, ass n tnekra"
  20,101,"Ad wekkôen dinna. Ay dir ip fellasen ppaâbga, ass n tnekra"
  20,102,"Ass ideg ara d ûuven di lbuq, a d Nefser ibe$wviyen, zgezwen assen"
  20,103,"Ad swecwicen wa i wa: \"mraw kan i teqqimem"
  20,104,"Nekwni, Nif akw akken Nessen, ayen d qqaôen, mi sen inna yiwen umxallef degsen: \"teqqimem kan ibwass"
  20,105,"Steqsayen k $ef idurar. Ini: \"a ten Issebruzzaâ Mass iw, d iwzan"
  20,106,A ten Irr d aza$aô ibuôen
  20,107,"Ur tepwaliv degs i iâawjen, ne$ i izzren"
  20,108,"Assen, ad vefôen aberraê, war zzrug. Ad irs ûûut zdat Uênin, a ppeslev kan i uswecwec"
  20,109,"Assen, ur ten tenfaâ ccafuâa, siwa i win Iooa Uênin, u Iôuva t $ef wawal"
  20,110,"Issen i illan zdat sen, i illan deffir sen. Ur illi sanda ara T issinen"
  20,111,Ad îîinzen wudmawen i Umuddir n lebda. Ara ixesôen d win ibubben ddens
  20,112,"Win ixeddmen ayen ilhan, u neppa iumen, ur ippagwad ddens, ne$ aqhaô"
  20,113,"Akka, Nessers it id, d Leqwôan s taâôabt. Nenewwel ed, degs, aâeggen, amar ad êezben, u a ten id ias usmekti"
  20,114,"D Ameqwôan Öebbi, Agellid, Tidep. Ur pêiri, di t$uôi, uqbel ma ifukk uweêêi s, $uôek. Ini: \"a Mass iw! Ernu yi di tmusni"
  20,115,"Ni$ Nâahed, zik, Adem. Ippu, ur Nufi $uôes laâzem"
  20,116,"Mi Nenna i lmalayek: \"knumt i Adem\", knant, siwa Iblis i iugin"
  20,117,"Nenna: \"a Adem, wagi, s tidep, d acengu k, akked tmeîîut ik. £urwat a kwen id issuffe$, si Loennet, a p$weblem"
  20,118,"Ih, keçç, degs, ur teplaéev, ur tâarruv"
  20,119,"S tidep, keçç, degs, ur tepfadev, ur k iîîuôôu yiîij"
  20,120,"I$wa t Cciîan, inna: \"a Adem, ad ak ssekne$ ttejôa uwekkeô, akw n tgelda n lebda"
  20,121,"Eççan segs, d$a walan iman nnsen âaryan, bdan la tessôen iman nnsen, s iferrawen n Loennet. Adem iaâûa Mass is, idda di le$wlav"
  20,122,"Sinna, Ifren it Mass is, Issuref as, Inha t"
  20,123,"Inna: \"ûûubet segs akw, wa d acengu n wa. Ma tusa kwen id nnhaya, s$uôI, win iddan d nnhaya iW, ur ipputellef, ur i$webbel"
  20,124,"Win iooan asmekti W, tameddurt is d tucmip. Ass n tnekra, a t Nefser d ader$al"
  20,125,"A d yini: \"a Mass iw! Acimi iyi Tfesrev d ader$al, ni$ lli$ pwali"
  20,126,"A d Yini: \"akken i k id iusan ssekniyen nne£, teppuv iten, akken ara tepwappuv, assa"
  20,127,"Akka ay Nepqeîîi win izegren tilas, ur numin s issekniyen n Mass is. U, s tidep, aâaqeb n laxeôt iwâaô kteô, u ad idum kteô"
  20,128,"Day ur ten inha ara wacêal isuta i Nesqucc, uqbel nnsen? La leêêun $ef tnezdu$in nnsen. Deg wayagi, s tidep, d issekniyen i imawlan n ddehn"
  20,129,"Lemmer ur d izwar ara wawal, s$uô Mass ik, akked lajel ipwassnen, yili, war ccekk, iûaô uâaqeb"
  20,130,"Ihi, bibb ayen d qqaôen, sbuccaâ s ccekôan Mass ik, uqbel ad inqeô yiîij, uqbel ad i$li, deg iv. Anez di levôuf n wass, amar fellak aôavi"
  20,131,"Ur ppara allen ik ar wayen i Nefka i kra n twaculin nnsen. D ajeooig n tmeddurt di ddunit, iwakken a ten Njeôôeb yis. A$iti n Mass ik yif it, u ad idum kteô"
  20,132,"Ameô taéallit i twacult ik, êerz ip. Ur ak Nessutur ôôeéq, d Nekwni ara k Iôeéqen. Laâquba d aêezzeb"
  20,133,"Nnan: \"a lemmer i $ d iusi s ussekni s$uô Mass is\"! Day ur ten id iusa ara ubeggen, deg wayen illan di tewôeqtin timezwura"
  20,134,"Lemmer iten Nesqucc s uqeîîi, uqbel neppa, a d inin, war ccekk: \"a Mass nne$! Acimi ur a$ d Tunzev ara amazan? A neddu d issekniyen iK, uqbel a nendell u a neppuqeîîi"
  20,135,"Ini: \"akw, la nepgani. Ihi gganit. A ppissinem anwi i iddan d ubrid ilhan, anwi i ipwanhan"